org.graalvm.polyglot

Enum HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping>
      • org.graalvm.polyglot.HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping>, java.lang.constant.Constable
    Enclosing class:
    HostAccess

    public static enum HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping
extends Enum<HostAccess.MutableTargetMapping>
    List of default host object mappings of mutable target types available in Value.as(Class). The mappings map guest object traits to host object types.
    Since:
    23.0
